Acting MD Koko Bello Launches Official Portrait For Public Consumption According to the statement, The acting Managing Director , Nigerian Ports Authority (NPA),has officially launched his portrait  for public consumption.  This was contained in a statement on Tuesday, from the Corporate and Strategic Communication department of the agency.  The statement said :”MOHAMMED BELLO KOKO, Ag Managing Director, NPA  ” Attached is the official Portrait of the Ag Managing Director NPA for your use,”the statement added.  “Koko Bello is currently the acting MD of the agency after the suspension of Hadiza Bala Usman.  The AmehNews recall that Koko Bello was the former Executive Director, Finance and Administration of NPA before his recent appointment.